\p ‚ÄúM…®r…® t âpo, Papa uya to' usewa'noma epuru pe te'ton kon an ânp…®t â'p â, Sanwer â, pu'kena' pe te'sen ena to' epuru pe pona r…®.\x - \xo 13:20 \xt Eseru Aimenkanin Nan 2:16; 1 Sanwer â 3:20\x* 
\v 21 M…®r…® a'tai, tepuru kon pe kin i'se ka'pon am â' esi'p â. M…®r…®pan Saar â, Kisi mu an âm â'p â Papa uya kin pe, m…®r…®pan uko'mam â'p â 40 kaisa r…® w âipiya to' epuru pe.\x - \xo 13:21 \xt 1 Sanwer â 8:5; 10:21\x* 
\v 22 Kin pe iye'to' yapai Saar â mo'ka t âuya t âpo, Papa uya Tepi' an âm â'p â kin pe. Wak â pe kuru Papa usaurok â'p â ip…®', ‚ÄòEposa' uya man warawo' Tepi', Ise'si mu upori'manin pe te'sen ku'nin, i'se e'to' ku'to' iya oton m…®r…®,‚Äô\f + \fr 13:22 \ft Eren 89:20\f* ta'p â Papa uya.\x - \xo 13:22 \xt 1 Sanwer â 13:14; 16:12\x* 
