\v 23 ‚ÄúPapa uya Tepi' pa r â'p â, Sises ennoko'p â Esuwer â am â' pika't…®se'na. M…®r…® kup â uya ta'p â t âuya utamokori ton p…®' aw…®r…®.  
\v 24 Sises e'sara't…® e't ârawasoman p…®' raw…®r…®, Isaan uya itekare ekama'p â tanporon kon Esuwer â awon kon p…®', …®ri t ânkup ân â kon apai to' era't…®to' pe, m…®r…®pan kon epa'taisimato' pe.\x - \xo 13:24 \xt Ma' 1:4; …Ñru' 3:3\x* 
\v 25 T ât ârawasooi i'ma'ka t âuya win…®k âi', Isaan uya to' ekama'pop…®t â'p â, ‚Äò∆ón â' pe uku'at âu? Ka'pon ennoko uya m…®r…®, tasa' r â'p â Papa uya ip…®' pe, uyekama auya'nokon ser…®, e'tane etat…®', ser…® pe r…® iyep â m…®r…® e'tane isapatooi m â' ara'ka poken p âra r…® esi,‚Äô ta'p â iya.\x - \xo 13:25 \xt Isaan 1:20; Ma'siu 3:11; Ma' 1:7; …Ñru' 3:16; Isaan 1:27\x* 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúUtonpa ton Esuwer â am â', Ep âra'an payan n â'san, Esuwer â am â' pen n…® n…®r…® Papa namanin nan, etat…®'! Ur…®'nokon iwano' pe kuru Papa uya epika't…®n n…®to' eseru ennoko'p â.  
\v 27 Surusiran pon kon ka'pon am â' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® to' epuru ton uya i'tu p âra iyesi'p â p âse r…® Sises esi pika't…®nin pe tukai', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® pu'kena' am â' maimu Sapa' kaisa r…® t âusekamasen to'ka'n âk â to' uya p âra iyesi'p â, e'tane pu'kena' am â' uya ekama'p â aw…®r…® to' uya iw…®n…®'p â.  
\v 28 Tu'kan kon n…® ka'pon am â' usaurok â'p â, ‚Äò∆óri kup â Sises uya,‚Äô tukai', e'tane iw…®to' ip…®k…®r…® oton eporo to' uya p âra iyesi'p â. M…®r…® r…® e'tane, itepuru Paire' ekama'po'p â to' uya ima'tan â'to' pe iya.\x - \xo 13:28 \xt Ma'siu 27:22-23; Ma' 15:13-14; …Ñru' 23:21-23; Isaan 19:15\x* 
\v 29 Pena r…® pu'kena' ton nekama'p â kup â'p â ka'pon am â' uya m…®r…® Sises p…®'. To' uya iw…®n…®'p â. Kurusu' pona to' uya ipokap…®t â'p â, m…®r…®pan mo'ka'p â t âron kon uya kurusu' poi, m…®r…®pan emaika'p â to' uya t…®' akasa' uruwai' pe ya'.\x - \xo 13:29 \xt Ma'siu 27:57-61; Ma' 15:42-47; …Ñru' 23:50-56; Isaan 19:38-42\x* 
\v 30 E'tane Papa uya i'm â'sa'ka'p â eri'n…®to' apai.  
\v 31 Inke r…® isenpoikap…®t â'p â ta'k…®r…® Kiyarari ponsi'k…® Surusiran pona it…®sa' kon enu ya', ka'pon am â' si ennin n â'san esi m…®r…® t âron kon ka'pon am â' pana ya' ekama p…®'.\x - \xo 13:31 \xt Inkup â'p â 1:3\x* 
