\v 34 Papa uya t âmu i'm â'sa'ka'p â iyeri'sa' apai, m…®r…®pan eri'to' oton pen n…® m…®r…® enta'. M…®r…® p…®', Papa uya utamokori kon am â' auro'ka'p â, 
\q1 ‚Äú‚Äò∆ópika't…® uya 'nokon kuru m…®r…®, umunk…® am â', 
