\v 35 Tepi' uya K ârai\f + \fr 13:35 \fq K ârai \ft (Kiri' maimu yau), m…®r…® pe p âra \fq Me'saya \ft (Ipuru maimu yau), asa'r…® r…® mar…® iyesi, \fq Papa Nan âm ân â \ft ta e'kwa pe.\f* p…®' Papa auro'kasa' t âron n…® Eren yau, 
